            <h3>What These Services Offer</h3>
            <p>
                Advisory services in Germany are focused on assisting international professionals with key needs:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Support with recognising foreign qualifications</li>
                <li>Advice on employment and vocational training</li>
                <li>Information about local laws, integration, and living</li>
                <li>Points of contact for regional job, training, and language support</li>
                <li>Dedicated services for newcomers and their families</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Local Chambers of Industry and Commerce, international offices of universities, and Welcome Centers
                are among the main contact points providing these services. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}
            </p>
